name: Naturally Foaming Facial Cleanser 5oz
description: Exactly what you need in a cleanser and nothing more. Lightly foaming and provides a deep thorough cleanse without over-drying. Ingredients: Aqua, Potassium Cocoate, Glycerin, Polysorbate-20, 1,2-Hexanediol, Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Oil, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) Oil, Litsea Cubeba (May Chang) Fruit Oil
